channel.title: Rev 194
channel.description:
So I've been looking at a deob'd 194 client (this was RuneScapes beta client), and I've found a bit of a problem. No darn maps are in the cache. It has basically everything it needs but maps. I really don't want to load 317 maps, due to it not being a proper 194, and that it wouldn't work correctly (317 objects without the support).
So basically, has anyone got any ideas? Or the 194 maps (prob. impossible)?
